    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Spice up your everyday stir-fry with a splash of gochujang. You'll sizzle juicy chicken and veg before tossing in spicy, savoury gochujang sauce and serving over white rice. It's the perfect speedy dinner. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
